4Geeks Academy offers a Data Science and Machine Learning course designed for beginners, aiming to equip participants with essential skills for careers in AI and machine learning. The program spans 16 weeks, with three weekly classes capped at 12 students. Participants will learn Python, SQL, and various statistical techniques, alongside constructing predictive models using industry-standard libraries and algorithms. No previous experience is required, and instruction is available in English and Spanish. Successful graduates receive a recognized certificate. For additional details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop